data.description: APPROVED OFFER WAITING SIGNED DOCUMENTS - REDUCED ANOTHER $24,900 - Roxshire - 4 bedrooms, 2 full/2 half baths, brick front 2 story, built 1989 on .54 acre corner lot - 3 levels of bright finished space - 1ST Floor includes formal dining room, living room with French doors, large eat-in kitchen with loads of cabinets, granite counters and island and access to rear screen porch, family room with raised panel trim, built in bookcases and opens to Florida room with additional door to screen porch, half bath - 2ND floor includes very large primary bedroom with walk-in closet and attached full bath with double vanity, tub and shower - second bedroom provides access to large walk-up floored attic - 2 additional bedrooms plus full bath - BASEMENT includes additional great room, rec room, laundry with chute, half bath, utility room, and access to 2 car side load garage with work bench - Rear of house includes multi-tiered deck, screened porch, and patio - Great quiet location, great schools, and easy access to shopping, restaurants, gas, Robius Rd, I-288, Courthouse Rd, Midlothian Tpke - Price reflects current condition as it will need some TLC for painting and flooring.
